            <title>[LU-4808] sanity tests cleanup to work on Xeon Phi</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4808</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Made the test_74c robust to different platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fix an issue with values more than 2^32 (for example 9.36473e+09).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fix an integer comparison in case of empty variable.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Check for tools presents (rsync and getfattr).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Check for CLIENTONLY mode.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Remove &quot;-x&quot; options from greep (it&apos;s not always supported).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Condding style cleanup.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
